A Kenyan tycoon is said to have stolen the heart of a Nigerian songstress. The two are said to be in a passionate and enduring affair that has lasted two years or so. The married tycoon is known for his striking good looks and unlimited wallet resources. At one time, during the Nigerian diva's birthday, the tycoon spared no expenses. He threw her a Sh3 million birthday party at the Coast. According to sources, the African queen meet the tycoon when she was in the country for a mega performance and she was later invited to perform for the tycoon in a private party, where she was paid top dollar. 